                "imgDesc": "<p>Iktomisaurs can <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Hold to Aim, entering the Spiritspeaker state</span>. In this state, they can absorb Phlogiston from objects within their field of vision. In addition, they can cause some special graffiti or objects with special Phlogiston Engravings to appear for a short time.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/2"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character97663",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/11/18/a8c207233701f52d6e4770154b44037b_7394151783094314843.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>When Iktomisaurs <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Hold</span> to perform their leap, they can <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">consume Phlogiston</span> to leap up <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">even higher</span>. For this reason, it's important for them to have a wide field of vision.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/2"
              }
